name: CODE COMMIT COFFEE PROFIT
description:
CODE COMMIT COFFEE PROFIT

This is the game where your willpower is tested!

Commit your changes, code, drink some coffee and try to fulfill your task in given time. If you can do it, you are an animal and your willpower is stronger than anyone else!

- This game is made for Xamk Game Jam II in 48 hours -

May the willpower be with you!
